			"details": "A smart contract to securely pass on assets if the owner becomes inactive. * Mechanism: 1. Owner deposits funds. 2. Owner must call `ping()` periodically (e.g., once a year). 3. If `ping()` is NOT called within the timeout period, the Beneficiary can claim the funds. Easy Deployment: No constructor arguments required.",
